7.jpg" /><br /><br />COLUMBUS, Ohio – Led by junior Griffin Lake's third-place finish in the smallbore competition, the West Virginia University rifle team sits in fourth place after the opening day of the 2026 NCAA Rifle Championships, hosted by Ohio State inside the Covelli Center in Columbus.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/13/DSC07987.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/13/DSC07987.jpg"><media:title>Griffin Lake</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/13/DSC07987.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 15:44:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>8</s:sport_id><s:story_id>58858</s:story_id></item></channel></rss>